  "description": "Portable Device Interface (PDI) framework stack for easy configurable applications running over avr, esp devices. Designed to enable/disable services such as WiFi, HTTP, MQTT, SFTP, SSH server, Telnet server, OTA, GPIO, Serial, cmd and much more handled with configurable Task Scheduler.",
